name: Praying for Peace in 2022
description:
The artist is 9 year old Toy Master and this is his message.

"I want my military uncles, cousins and all the soldiers to have peace in the world so they can come home to their kids and moms and be loved, because everyone misses you."  

Toy Master has several relatives currently serving in the Army, Navy and Air Force. 

This artwork is being submitted for the #HENjackpot  "Rocking New Year JACKPOT" event. Find event info at this link  https://twitter.com/rblbab/status/1469650566439931906
